Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.73,0:00:02.42,中文,,0,0,0,,吸血鬼日记 前情回顾\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Previously on "The Vampire Diaries"...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.42,0:00:03.79,中文,,0,0,0,,达蒙死了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Damon is gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.79,0:00:06.18,中文,,0,0,0,,我要你催眠我 让我忘记我曾爱过他\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I want you to compel me to forget that I ever loved him.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.18,0:00:09.01,中文,,0,0,0,,-达蒙萨瓦托尔是谁 -他就是个畜生\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}- Who is Damon Salvatore? - He's a monster.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.01,0:00:10.46,中文,,0,0,0,,要回家 我们就得利用一个古设备\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}To get home, we'll harness the power
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.46,0:00:12.60,中文,,0,0,0,,来吸收日蚀的力量\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}of the eclipse using a mystical relic.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.60,0:00:13.70,中文,,0,0,0,,不\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.58,0:00:19.30,中文,,0,0,0,,我的妻子被吸血鬼杀了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Vampires murdered my wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.30,0:00:21.75,中文,,0,0,0,,我要靠他找出他的其他吸血鬼朋友\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I'm gonna get him to name all his vampire buddies.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.75,0:00:23.12,中文,,0,0,0,,需要帮助吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Need any help?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.99,0:00:30.16,中文,,0,0,0,,如果你心底还有一点点\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}If even just a small, little part of you
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.16,0:00:32.49,中文,,0,0,0,,是想回来看我的话\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}came back to check on me,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.49,0:00:34.22,中文,,0,0,0,,那就留下来吧\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}then stay.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.82,0:00:37.13,中文,,0,0,0,,我过的不好 达蒙\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Not doing so great, Damon.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.13,0:00:39.28,中文,,0,0,0,,我不知道该怎么办\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I'm lost, brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.51,0:00:42.97,中文,,0,0,0,,说来话长 弟弟\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}It's kind of a long story, brother,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.97,0:00:44.51,中文,,0,0,0,,但是我还是回来了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}but I'm back.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.42,0:00:54.45,中文,,0,0,0,,求你放我走\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Please just let me go.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.45,0:00:56.45,中文,,0,0,0,,我知道这看起来有点血腥暴力\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I know this may seem a little barbaric,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.45,0:00:59.53,中文,,0,0,0,,但是我保证 不会滥用私刑\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}but I promise you, it's nothing personal.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.99,0:01:02.82,中文,,0,0,0,,你为什么要这么做\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Why are you doing this?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.82,0:01:04.66,中文,,0,0,0,,我们可没有这么多时间来解释这个\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}It's a longer story than we have time for,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.66,0:01:08.54,中文,,0,0,0,,但是 相信我 你也不想过这样的生活\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}but... trust me... you don't want this life...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.70,0:01:11.57,中文,,0,0,0,,如果这还能叫做生活的话\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}If you can call it that.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.20,0:01:19.64,中文,,0,0,0,,再加把劲\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}All right. Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.64,0:01:23.08,中文,,0,0,0,,快 快\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Come on. Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.08,0:01:26.25,中文,,0,0,0,,快\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.89,0:01:34.26,中文,,0,0,0,,怎么回事 怎么回事 啊\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}What's that? What is that? Aah!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.26,0:01:38.54,中文,,0,0,0,,到底是怎么了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}What is happening? Aah!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.68,0:01:47.57,中文,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.91,0:01:54.61,中文,,0,0,0,,-我也很想你 -难以置信\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}- I missed you, too, buddy. - I can't believe it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.31,0:01:58.35,中文,,0,0,0,,我以为你走了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I thought you were gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.35,0:02:00.91,中文,,0,0,0,,你不会以为我死了的那种走吧\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}You didn't think I was gone gone, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.92,0:02:03.28,中文,,0,0,0,,我发誓要给你永生的折磨\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Promised you an eternity of misery.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.28,0:02:05.45,中文,,0,0,0,,哈哈\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Ha ha!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.45,0:02:06.90,中文,,0,0,0,,他回来了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}He's back?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.89,0:02:10.99,中文,,0,0,0,,-怎么回来的 -我不知道\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}- How? - I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.99,0:02:12.53,中文,,0,0,0,,说实在的 他说达蒙回来了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Honestly, everything Stefan said
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.53,0:02:15.23,中文,,0,0,0,,之后的每句话我都心不在焉了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}after, "Damon is back," Is kind of a blur.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.23,0:02:16.49,中文,,0,0,0,,邦妮呢\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}What about Bonnie?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.49,0:02:19.90,中文,,0,0,0,,她牺牲了自己 我才得以回来\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}She sacrificed herself so I can come back.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.90,0:02:21.44,中文,,0,0,0,,我不想其他人知道\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I don't want anyone to know.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.44,0:02:22.70,中文,,0,0,0,,不可以再让大家都痛苦了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}There's no sense making this harder
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.70,0:02:24.00,中文,,0,0,0,,大家都够烦的了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}than it already is.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.01,0:02:26.27,中文,,0,0,0,,那我们要怎么告诉其他人\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}What are we gonna tell people?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.27,0:02:28.74,中文,,0,0,0,,他说邦妮没和他在一起\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}He said that she wasn't over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.74,0:02:31.41,中文,,0,0,0,,那他是在哪里\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Where is there, exactly?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.41,0:02:34.61,中文,,0,0,0,,-1994年的神秘瀑布镇 -我知道很难相信\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}- Mystic Falls, 1994? - I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.62,0:02:36.12,中文,,0,0,0,,女巫们结合她们的力量\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}A bunch of witches were gonna get together
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.12,0:02:38.29,中文,,0,0,0,,创造了一个时空监狱\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}and create some space-time purgatory,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.29,0:02:39.79,中文,,0,0,0,,我也希望她们挑的时间能好一点\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}you'd think they'd pick a better year than
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.79,0:02:42.22,中文,,0,0,0,,而不是选了科特柯本自杀的那年\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}the one that Kurt Cobain killed himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.22,0:02:44.46,中文,,0,0,0,,整件事情真是太折磨人了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Whole thing was just very depressing.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.46,0:02:46.76,中文,,0,0,0,,那你是怎么回来的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}So how did you get back?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.76,0:02:48.36,中文,,0,0,0,,说来话长 我眼前闪过一大片闪光\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Long story... big flash of light,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.36,0:02:49.73,中文,,0,0,0,,现在还有二十年的时差还没倒回来\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}two decades' worth of jet lag.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.73,0:02:51.46,中文,,0,0,0,,等回家了我再跟你说\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I will explain all of my adventures
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.47,0:02:53.20,中文,,0,0,0,,我的离奇遭遇 但是现在\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}in that flannel hellscape, but first,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.20,0:02:55.94,中文,,0,0,0,,我赶着去见个人\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}there's someone I got to go see.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.94,0:02:58.34,中文,,0,0,0,,我不想见到他\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I don't want to see him.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.34,0:03:00.41,中文,,0,0,0,,我明白\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I get it,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.41,0:03:02.22,中文,,0,0,0,,但是你现在就是这么想的 埃琳娜\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}but that's how you feel now, Elena.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.71,0:03:04.08,中文,,0,0,0,,如果你认为你有一点点的机会能见到\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}If you thought there was even a chance
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.08,0:03:06.21,中文,,0,0,0,,达蒙的话 你是绝不会\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}you'd see Damon again, you would have never
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.21,0:03:08.59,中文,,0,0,0,,叫我催眠你忘记你和他之间的事的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}asked me to compel away your memories of loving him.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.59,0:03:10.82,中文,,0,0,0,,她做了什么\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}She did what?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.82,0:03:13.49,中文,,0,0,0,,她叫阿拉里克做的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}She had Alaric do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.49,0:03:16.82,中文,,0,0,0,,-达蒙会杀了我的 -你又杀不死\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}- Damon is going to kill me. - You're unkillable.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.83,0:03:18.27,中文,,0,0,0,,这并不意味着他不会试试看\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Doesn't mean he won't try.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.27,0:03:20.66,中文,,0,0,0,,你认为我见到他会怎么样\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}What do you think is gonna happen when I do see him?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.66,0:03:22.66,中文,,0,0,0,,我必须得去见她 斯特凡\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I just need to see her, Stefan.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.66,0:03:24.33,中文,,0,0,0,,我们的眼神交汇 催眠就会失效\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Our eyes will meet, fireworks will go off,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.33,0:03:26.77,中文,,0,0,0,,一切都会恢复正常\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}and the balance of nature will be restored.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.85,0:03:29.47,中文,,0,0,0,,她爱我\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}She loves me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.47,0:03:32.10,中文,,0,0,0,,-他就是个神经失常的杀人狂 -你这么想是因为\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}- He's a psychotic killer. - You only feel that way
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.11,0:03:33.74,中文,,0,0,0,,我把关于他的好的记忆都抹掉了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}because I erased all the good parts.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.74,0:03:36.56,中文,,0,0,0,,我看不到他有什么好可以抵消掉他的坏\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I don't see anything that could balance out the bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.70,0:03:40.51,中文,,0,0,0,,答应我 不要解除催眠\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Promise me you won't lift the compulsion.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.51,0:03:43.62,中文,,0,0,0,,-答应我 -我不会的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}- Promise me. - I won't, ok,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.62,0:03:45.62,中文,,0,0,0,,除非是你要求 好吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}not until you ask me to,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.62,0:03:48.39,中文,,0,0,0,,-谢谢 -但是 埃琳娜\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}- thank you. - But, Elena,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.39,0:03:50.24,中文,,0,0,0,,我希望你能叫我解除催眠\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I hope you ask me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.82,0:03:53.29,中文,,0,0,0,,我得走了 还得去医院值班\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I have to go. I have a shift at the hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.29,0:03:56.00,中文,,0,0,0,,-从什么时候开始你要值班了 -从达蒙回来那一刻开始\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}- Since when? - Since Damon came back
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.00,0:03:57.53,中文,,0,0,0,,我会不顾一切地躲着他\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}and I'm trying desperately to avoid him.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.53,0:04:00.03,中文,,0,0,0,,好吧 如果你要躲着谁的话\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Fine, but if you're avoiding people,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.03,0:04:02.44,中文,,0,0,0,,顺便也躲着乔吧\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}add Jo to your list.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.44,0:04:03.84,中文,,0,0,0,,那天晚上我试着催眠\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I compelled her to forget our date
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.84,0:04:05.64,中文,,0,0,0,,她忘了我们的约会 没用\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}the other night, and it didn't take.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.64,0:04:07.04,中文,,0,0,0,,没用是什么意思\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}What do you mean, it didn't take?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.04,0:04:10.28,中文,,0,0,0,,要不她就是服了马鞭草 要不然就是别的原因\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Well, either she's on vervain or there's some other reason,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.28,0:04:12.01,中文,,0,0,0,,总而言之 我们催眠不了她\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}but she can't be compelled.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.01,0:04:17.65,中文,,0,0,0,,-你试试看能不能找到原因 -好\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}- So see if you can find out why. - Ok. Yeah. I will.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.65,0:04:20.35,中文,,0,0,0,,你会打电话给杰里米吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Will you call Jeremy?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.35,0:04:23.46,中文,,0,0,0,,我得跟他说说邦妮的事\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I had to tell him about Bonnie over the phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.46,0:04:27.53,中文,,0,0,0,,你也能想到他的反应了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}You can imagine how that went.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.29,0:04:31.63,中文,,0,0,0,,-你要去哪 -要出去\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}- Where are you going? - Out.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.63,0:04:33.60,中文,,0,0,0,,你答应过我会帮我找到我的亲戚的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}You promised me you'd help me track down my relatives.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.60,0:04:36.30,中文,,0,0,0,,晚点 好吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Just... later, ok?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.30,0:04:38.87,中文,,0,0,0,,杰里米 你不能说了一句 扎克萨瓦托尔是你爸爸\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Jeremy, you can't just say, "Zach Salvatore was your dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.87,0:04:40.87,中文,,0,0,0,,遗憾的是他死了 然后就出去吧\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Too bad he's dead," And then, "Peace out."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.87,0:04:42.71,中文,,0,0,0,,现在我没时间帮你找亲戚\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I can't do this right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.71,0:04:44.41,中文,,0,0,0,,是什么事这么紧急让你\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}What is so urgent to make you
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.41,0:04:46.71,中文,,0,0,0,,终于舍得把屁股从沙发上挪开了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}finally unglue your ass from the couch?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.71,0:04:49.41,中文,,0,0,0,,我知道不是学校的事 也不是工作\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I know it's not school. It's not work.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.42,0:04:51.95,中文,,0,0,0,,如果是有关另一个女生的话 那我想先去洗个澡\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}If it's another girl, I'd shower first.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.72,0:04:57.98,中文,,0,0,0,,我只是想离开这里\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I just need to get out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.23,0:05:09.10,中文,,0,0,0,,特里普的跑腿仔回来了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Tripp's errand boy returns.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.14,0:05:14.61,中文,,0,0,0,,哦 我的错\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Ooh, my bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.61,0:05:16.91,中文,,0,0,0,,没事 兄弟\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Heh. That's all right, mate.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.91,0:05:18.11,中文,,0,0,0,,你靠过来一点\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Just lean in,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.11,0:05:19.44,中文,,0,0,0,,然后我就可以自己喝了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}and I'll take it right from the tap.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.45,0:05:21.48,中文,,0,0,0,,这个就不用了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I'll pass.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.48,0:05:23.88,中文,,0,0,0,,就这点\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Yeah? Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.88,0:05:26.78,中文,,0,0,0,,我得恢复体力 你才能帮我逃走\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I'm gonna need my strength back for when you help me escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.78,0:05:29.52,中文,,0,0,0,,对不起 如果是斯特凡帮忙抓你的话 那我想你是罪有应得\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Sorry. If Stefan turned you in, I'm guessing you deserved it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.79,0:05:34.57,中文,,0,0,0,,什么时候斯特凡成了道德标杆了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}When did Stefan's moral compass become the new true north?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.39,0:05:37.23,中文,,0,0,0,,不是他逃去一个\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Wasn't he the one who scurried off
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.23,0:05:39.06,中文,,0,0,0,,无名小镇吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}to some poxy, little town while he
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.06,0:05:40.43,中文,,0,0,0,,他还让所有人以为\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}let everyone believe he was still
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.43,0:05:42.53,中文,,0,0,0,,他还在努力找他哥哥\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}searching for his brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.54,0:05:45.27,中文,,0,0,0,,要我说 这可不是什么豪言壮举啊\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Not exactly the hero move, if you ask me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.27,0:05:47.14,中文,,0,0,0,,我还是认为把你关在这里\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Still, I think the general population
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.14,0:05:48.71,中文,,0,0,0,,大家的人身安全才更有保障\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}is safer with you in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.71,0:05:50.58,中文,,0,0,0,,好吧 可能你说得对\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Yeah. Probably right,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.58,0:05:52.81,中文,,0,0,0,,除了埃琳娜\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}well, except for Elena...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.81,0:05:55.91,中文,,0,0,0,,斯特凡 卡罗琳 还有你\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Stefan, Caroline, you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.92,0:05:57.82,中文,,0,0,0,,你认为我把你知道吸血鬼的事\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}What do you think would happen if I
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.82,0:06:00.75,中文,,0,0,0,,告诉你老板\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}were to tell your boss about known vampires
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.75,0:06:03.35,中文,,0,0,0,,他会怎么做\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}and their groupies?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.72,0:06:09.26,中文,,0,0,0,,去萨凡纳这一趟就是在浪费汽油\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Well, Savannah was a waste of gas.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.26,0:06:11.93,中文,,0,0,0,,有那么几个血袋 但是你跟我们说的房子\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Minus a few blood bags, the house you told us about
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.93,0:06:13.63,中文,,0,0,0,,是空的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}was empty.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.63,0:06:16.57,中文,,0,0,0,,真奇怪 他们肯定是收到风提前逃走了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Odd. Must have smelled you coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.57,0:06:18.60,中文,,0,0,0,,幸好我遇到一个女生\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Hmm, would have been a total bust,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.60,0:06:20.64,中文,,0,0,0,,她和你描述的一模一样\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}except I happened upon a girl
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.64,0:06:23.51,中文,,0,0,0,,要不然这一趟就一无所获了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}that fit the description that you gave me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.51,0:06:26.18,中文,,0,0,0,,是在靠近惠特默尔学院抓到的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}That was near Whitmore,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.18,0:06:30.89,中文,,0,0,0,,但是离你说的地方有50英里\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}500 miles from where you said she was gonna be.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.35,0:06:35.65,中文,,0,0,0,,-是艾薇吗 -就是她\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}- Is this Ivy? - That's the one.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.65,0:06:38.66,中文,,0,0,0,,我再给你一天时间想清楚\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}So I'm gonna give you today to conjure up
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.66,0:06:40.96,中文,,0,0,0,,你的吸血鬼朋友们在哪\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}the location of your vampire friends,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.96,0:06:44.33,中文,,0,0,0,,要不然我可要带你去神秘瀑布镇\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}or you and I are gonna go sightseeing
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.33,0:06:47.73,中文,,0,0,0,,走一趟了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}in Mystic Falls.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.70,0:06:59.94,中文,,0,0,0,,你为什么不告诉我们\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Why didn't you tell us Enzo has been
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.95,0:07:01.45,中文,,0,0,0,,恩佐一直都被关着呢\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}locked up this whole time?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.45,0:07:03.48,中文,,0,0,0,,说真的 我不觉得有谁关心他\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Honestly, I didn't know anybody was missing him.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.48,0:07:05.38,中文,,0,0,0,,-马特 -抱歉\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}- Matt! - I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.38,0:07:07.52,中文,,0,0,0,,我实在是搞不清楚现在我们喜欢的是谁\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I was confused about which vampires we like
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.52,0:07:09.02,中文,,0,0,0,,讨厌的又是谁\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}and which ones we don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.02,0:07:13.02,中文,,0,0,0,,那艾薇呢 她是不是也在那\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Ok. Well, what about Ivy? Is she there, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.02,0:07:16.53,中文,,0,0,0,,特里普把她和另外两个吸血鬼载过边境了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Tripp drove her and two others across the border last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.53,0:07:19.20,中文,,0,0,0,,天哪\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Oh, God.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.20,0:07:21.50,中文,,0,0,0,,那你知不知道特里普现在在哪\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Well, do you know where Tripp is now?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.50,0:07:22.83,中文,,0,0,0,,他在跟另一条线索\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}He's running down another lead,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.83,0:07:24.03,中文,,0,0,0,,但是他没告诉我是什么线索\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}but he didn't tell me what it was.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.04,0:07:25.54,中文,,0,0,0,,你能去找一下是什么吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Well, can you find out?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.54,0:07:27.07,中文,,0,0,0,,我们得弄清楚他的下一个目标是谁\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}We need to know who his next target is.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.07,0:07:29.67,中文,,0,0,0,,如果恩佐同意说的话 下个目标就是你们\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}If Enzo talks, it'll be you guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.67,0:07:31.54,中文,,0,0,0,,那是不可能的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Well, that's not going to happen
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.54,0:07:33.34,中文,,0,0,0,,因为我们会把他救出来 是不是\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}because we're busting him out, right,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.34,0:07:35.71,中文,,0,0,0,,那样我才能臭骂这没用的家伙竟然被逮到了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}if for no other reason than so I can kick his ass
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.71,0:07:37.55,中文,,0,0,0,,然后再把他揍一顿\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}for getting caught in the first place.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.55,0:07:39.25,中文,,0,0,0,,你知不知道特里普\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}You have any idea how he even managed
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.25,0:07:41.32,中文,,0,0,0,,是怎么抓到他的吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}to get his hands on it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.32,0:07:44.51,中文,,0,0,0,,他才抓不到 是我抓的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}He didn't. I turned him in.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.40,0:07:58.30,中文,,0,0,0,,谁\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Who is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.30,0:08:00.77,中文,,0,0,0,,是我\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Hey, it's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.77,0:08:04.14,中文,,0,0,0,,我有话要跟你说\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I just wanted to talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.14,0:08:07.20,中文,,0,0,0,,现在我没空\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I can't, not now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.85,0:08:12.48,中文,,0,0,0,,我知道你为什么要这么做\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Look. I know why you did what you did.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.48,0:08:14.88,中文,,0,0,0,,那都不是真的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}It's not real.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.89,0:08:18.81,中文,,0,0,0,,你知道什么是真的吗 你对我的感觉就是真的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}You know what's real? The way you felt for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.18,0:08:22.59,中文,,0,0,0,,你曾经跟我说这是你这辈子\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}You once told me that it was the most real thing
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.59,0:08:24.82,中文,,0,0,0,,感受到的最真实的事了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}you ever felt in your life.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.43,0:08:33.10,中文,,0,0,0,,-现在这些感觉都没了 -拜托 埃琳娜\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}- Those feelings are gone. - Oh, come on, Elena.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.10,0:08:35.76,中文,,0,0,0,,你也催眠过别人\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}You've compelled enough people to know
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.31,0:08:39.38,中文,,0,0,0,,那只能掩盖真相\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}it's just a way of covering the truth,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.38,0:08:42.48,中文,,0,0,0,,无论你多想要掩盖真相\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}and no matter how badly you want it done,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.48,0:08:46.00,中文,,0,0,0,,谎言还是谎言\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}it doesn't make it any less of a lie,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.74,0:08:49.25,中文,,0,0,0,,你知道吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.59,0:08:59.67,中文,,0,0,0,,我听到你的呼吸了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Oh, I hear you breathing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.89,0:09:05.39,中文,,0,0,0,,你不知道我想听到你的呼吸想了多久\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}You have no idea how long I've wanted to hear you breathe.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.85,0:09:21.72,中文,,0,0,0,,开门吧 埃琳娜\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Just open the door, Elena.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.95,0:09:26.29,中文,,0,0,0,,一切都会回归正轨的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Everything can go back to the way it was.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.66,0:09:33.72,中文,,0,0,0,,就\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Just...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.97,0:09:38.09,中文,,0,0,0,,开门就好了 埃琳娜\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Just open the door, Elena, please...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.21,0:09:43.37,中文,,0,0,0,,那你至少走开点\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Or, at the very least, step aside
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.37,0:09:45.71,中文,,0,0,0,,因为我准备破门而入了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}because I'm gonna kick this door in.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.41,0:10:27.01,中文,,0,0,0,,真的吗 你真的跳窗逃走了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Seriously? You jumped out of a window?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.01,0:10:28.14,中文,,0,0,0,,如果被别人看到了怎么办\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}What if somebody saw you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.14,0:10:31.21,中文,,0,0,0,,我知道 我知道 我很害怕 我也不知道怎么做\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I know, I know. I panicked. I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.21,0:10:33.17,中文,,0,0,0,,他在那已经被困了好几个月了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Look. He's been trapped over there alone for months.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.17,0:10:34.47,中文,,0,0,0,,他就是想见见你\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}He just wants to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.47,0:10:36.97,中文,,0,0,0,,我知道我应该有什么感觉\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Look. I get how I'm supposed to feel,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.97,0:10:41.34,中文,,0,0,0,,但是我也感受到了我的真的感觉 我现在很开心\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}but I know how I actually feel, and I'm happy now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.34,0:10:43.44,中文,,0,0,0,,如果我看到了他 然后我的感觉\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}What if I look at him and my old feelings
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.44,0:10:44.94,中文,,0,0,0,,都冲破催眠重新回来了怎么办\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}break through the compulsion?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.95,0:10:46.31,中文,,0,0,0,,不会的 如果真的会\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Well, they won't, but even if they did,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.31,0:10:48.65,中文,,0,0,0,,也不是一件坏事啊\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}is that such a bad thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.65,0:10:53.12,中文,,0,0,0,,是啊 我就像你一样重新开始了 好吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Yeah. I started over just like you did, ok?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.12,0:10:54.99,中文,,0,0,0,,我为我自己 还有我的未来\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I made a smart choice for myself
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.99,0:10:57.76,中文,,0,0,0,,做出了明智的选择\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}and for my future.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.76,0:11:00.93,中文,,0,0,0,,斯特凡 我昨晚吻了利亚姆\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Stefan, I kissed Liam last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.93,0:11:04.50,中文,,0,0,0,,噢 请忘记你告诉了我这个\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Oh, please forget that you told me that
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.50,0:11:07.20,中文,,0,0,0,,而且千万不要把这个告诉达蒙\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}and definitely do not tell Damon that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.20,0:11:08.93,中文,,0,0,0,,因为他会杀了利亚姆的 是吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Because he's gonna kill him, right,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.94,0:11:11.20,中文,,0,0,0,,就像他杀了我的弟弟一样\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}just like he killed my brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.20,0:11:13.71,中文,,0,0,0,,我是想说 因为他肯定会心碎的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I was gonna say because he'll be heartbroken.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.71,0:11:15.01,中文,,0,0,0,,听着 你想做什么呢\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Listen. What do you want to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.01,0:11:16.48,中文,,0,0,0,,我是说 你最终还是得见他的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I mean, you have to see him eventually.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.48,0:11:19.14,中文,,0,0,0,,我知道 但是我就是没准备好\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I know, but I just don't think
