Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.65,0:11:23.48,中文,,0,0,0,,我没\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I'm not...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.48,0:11:27.69,中文,,0,0,0,,我就是没 准备好\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I'm just not... ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.69,0:11:29.72,中文,,0,0,0,,我要走了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I got to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.37,0:11:50.51,中文,,0,0,0,,- 埃琳娜  - 嘿\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}- Elena. - Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.51,0:11:52.08,中文,,0,0,0,,我还以为你今天不会来的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I didn't think you were here today.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.08,0:11:54.55,中文,,0,0,0,,嗯 是啊 我改变了计划\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Yeah. No. I changed my schedule around.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.55,0:11:58.42,中文,,0,0,0,,好吧 跟我来\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Ok. Follow me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.94,0:12:17.84,中文,,0,0,0,,莎拉 你在干嘛\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Sarah, what are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.84,0:12:19.70,中文,,0,0,0,,我可以问你同样的问题\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Could ask you the same question.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.71,0:12:21.34,中文,,0,0,0,,你不能来这儿\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}You can't be in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.34,0:12:24.18,中文,,0,0,0,,看你紧张的样子 要么你在下黄片\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}From the look on your face, either you're downloading porn
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.18,0:12:26.11,中文,,0,0,0,,要么就是你也不该来这儿\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}or you're not supposed to be here, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.11,0:12:28.95,中文,,0,0,0,,你在特里普的办公室干嘛\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}What are you doing in Tripp's office?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.95,0:12:30.45,中文,,0,0,0,,你想要什么\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}What do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.45,0:12:33.35,中文,,0,0,0,,一些以前住在这儿的人的信息\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Information on some people who used to live here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.35,0:12:35.15,中文,,0,0,0,,你知道塞尔瓦托家族的任何事情吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}You know anything about the Salvatores?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.15,0:12:36.62,中文,,0,0,0,,不太了解\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Not really.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.62,0:12:39.93,中文,,0,0,0,,好吧 杰里米说 扎克·塞尔瓦托是我的爸爸\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Well, according to Jeremy, Zach Salvatore was my dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.94,0:12:42.53,中文,,0,0,0,,都说他死于一次动物袭击\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}He supposedly died from an animal attack,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.53,0:12:44.76,中文,,0,0,0,,而且 碰巧的是 我妈妈也是死于动物袭击\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}and, coincidentally, so did my mom,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.76,0:12:46.80,中文,,0,0,0,,但是我关注好久了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}but I've been paying attention.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.80,0:12:48.47,中文,,0,0,0,,我知道这种说法是什么意思\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I know what that's code for,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.47,0:12:50.30,中文,,0,0,0,,而且你的老板似乎\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}and your boss seems to know a lot
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.30,0:12:52.80,中文,,0,0,0,,对致命的野生动物非常了解 所以\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}about homicidal wildlife, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.81,0:12:54.94,中文,,0,0,0,,所以你认为闯进来看看是个好主意\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}So you thought breaking in here was a good idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.94,0:12:57.14,中文,,0,0,0,,我猜你也有这种想法\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Guess we have that in common.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.14,0:12:59.28,中文,,0,0,0,,现在 要么你来帮我 要么当我告诉你老板\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Now, either you help me or start coming up
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.28,0:13:02.38,中文,,0,0,0,,你在偷查他资料的时候 想想找个什么借口好吧\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}with a good lie when I tell your boss you were snooping.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.58,0:13:08.45,中文,,0,0,0,,动物袭击案件的档案 都在那边\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Animal attacks are filed over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.36,0:13:15.66,中文,,0,0,0,,萨尔茨曼教授\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Professor Saltzman.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.66,0:13:19.36,中文,,0,0,0,,怎么 不能催眠你自己成为一个博士吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}What, couldn't compel yourself a Ph.D.?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.36,0:13:22.85,中文,,0,0,0,,-不敢相信你居然回来了 -是的哥回来了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}- I can't believe you're back. - I am. Heh.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.25,0:13:31.18,中文,,0,0,0,,-那么 你到底怎么样了 -嗯 让我们看看吧 里克\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}- So... how the hell are you? - Well, let's see, Ric.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.18,0:13:32.61,中文,,0,0,0,,我从某种旧式口袋状的小宇宙中\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I clawed my way
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.61,0:13:34.51,中文,,0,0,0,,连滚带爬逃出来\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}out of some retro pocket universe,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.51,0:13:36.88,中文,,0,0,0,,却发现我还要催眠自己\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}only to find that I needed to compel myself
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.88,0:13:38.28,中文,,0,0,0,,换个身份\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}a new change of clothes
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.28,0:13:40.99,中文,,0,0,0,,因为这个反魔法罩\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}because this antimagic hamster ball
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.99,0:13:42.95,中文,,0,0,0,,一直在阻止我回来\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}is keeping me from going home,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.95,0:13:44.72,中文,,0,0,0,,然后我又发现我最好的朋友\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}and then I find out that my best friend,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.72,0:13:46.39,中文,,0,0,0,,却对此无动于衷\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}rather than doing anything about it,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.39,0:13:49.39,中文,,0,0,0,,反而在这种时候\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}decided that it was the best use of his time
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.39,0:13:51.96,中文,,0,0,0,,催眠我美丽又可爱的女朋友\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}to compel my beautiful and lovely girlfriend
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.96,0:13:54.06,中文,,0,0,0,,让她忘记曾经爱过我\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}to forget that she ever loved me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.07,0:13:57.33,中文,,0,0,0,,哼 我真的很好 里克 谢谢你的关心\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Heh. I'm great, Ric. Thanks for asking.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.34,0:13:58.64,中文,,0,0,0,,听着 达蒙\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Look, Damon.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.64,0:14:00.50,中文,,0,0,0,,我知道的 她如果没有我 就会一团糟 好吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I know she was a train wreck without me, ok,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.51,0:14:03.71,中文,,0,0,0,,可是清除所有记忆 真的至于吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}but a full mind erase, seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.71,0:14:08.28,中文,,0,0,0,,她实在太爱你了 这份爱让她痛不欲生\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}She loved you too much, and it was killing her.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.28,0:14:10.54,中文,,0,0,0,,嗯 我感到很荣幸\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Well, I'm flattered,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.02,0:14:12.86,中文,,0,0,0,,但是我回来了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}but I'm back.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.52,0:14:16.35,中文,,0,0,0,,所以让我们\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}So let's get this uncompulsion
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.35,0:14:17.89,中文,,0,0,0,,把她的记忆恢复好吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}on the books, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.89,0:14:22.03,中文,,0,0,0,,好的 只要埃琳娜告诉我她想这样就行\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Fine, as soon as Elena tells me that what she wants.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.03,0:14:25.93,中文,,0,0,0,,嗯 那么问题来了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Right. Here's the thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.93,0:14:28.71,中文,,0,0,0,,如果她记不起为什么要恢复记忆\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}She's not gonna want to be uncompelled
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.71,0:14:32.80,中文,,0,0,0,,那她就不会想恢复记忆了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}if she can't remember why she'd want to be uncompelled.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.80,0:14:34.87,中文,,0,0,0,,嗯嗯 鸡生蛋蛋生鸡的循环\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Mm-hmm. Chicken, egg.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.87,0:14:38.09,中文,,0,0,0,,我知道 很遗憾\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I know, and I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.09,0:14:42.85,中文,,0,0,0,,遗憾 她连见都不想见我了 里克\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Sorry? She won't even see me, Ric.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.85,0:14:46.68,中文,,0,0,0,,我明白 达蒙 但她现在很开心\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I get it, Damon, but she's happy,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.68,0:14:48.62,中文,,0,0,0,,所以除非她要求我这么做\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}and I'm not gonna take that away from her
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.62,0:14:50.59,中文,,0,0,0,,否则我不会给她恢复记忆的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}until she asks me to.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.59,0:14:52.19,中文,,0,0,0,,我不是不想埃琳娜开心\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}It's not like I don't want Elena to be happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.19,0:14:54.66,中文,,0,0,0,,我只是想要她和我一起开心\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I just want her to be happy with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.53,0:14:59.86,中文,,0,0,0,,好吧\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.36,0:15:12.41,中文,,0,0,0,,看 恩佐并不是很小心\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Look. Enzo wasn't being careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.41,0:15:13.61,中文,,0,0,0,,特里普最终会抓住他的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Tripp would've caught him eventually,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.61,0:15:15.28,中文,,0,0,0,,那就意味着我们全都会有危险\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}and that meant danger for all of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.28,0:15:17.35,中文,,0,0,0,,真对 所以你交出了恩佐\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Right. So you handed Enzo over
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.35,0:15:18.95,中文,,0,0,0,,这样猎人就不会追杀我们了 现在\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}so we wouldn't be targeted, and now
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.95,0:15:21.58,中文,,0,0,0,,你又要救恩佐 猎人就又无法追杀我们了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}you're rescuing him so we won't be targeted.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.59,0:15:22.85,中文,,0,0,0,,你真是天才\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Way to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.85,0:15:23.95,中文,,0,0,0,,好吧 我以为特里普会杀了他\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Well, I thought Tripp was gonna kill him.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.95,0:15:26.29,中文,,0,0,0,,我没想到他会为了得到信息 而让他活着\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I didn't think he was gonna keep him alive for information.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.29,0:15:28.36,中文,,0,0,0,,噢 好吧 这样听起来\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Oh, well, in that case, sounds like you
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.36,0:15:30.06,中文,,0,0,0,,你还真是个实在人啊\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}were just being practical.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.06,0:15:32.43,中文,,0,0,0,,-所以你也出卖了艾薇 是吧 -什么\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}- So did you rat out Ivy, too? - What?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.43,0:15:33.96,中文,,0,0,0,,不是吗 你已经不想再和她交易\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Well, you didn't want to deal with her anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.96,0:15:35.26,中文,,0,0,0,,你想要她消失 她还真消失了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}You wanted her gone, and now she is.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.27,0:15:36.63,中文,,0,0,0,,你知道么\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}You know what?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.63,0:15:37.90,中文,,0,0,0,,你真该对特里普说谢谢\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}You really should write Tripp a thank-you note.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.90,0:15:39.57,中文,,0,0,0,,慢着慢着 恩佐转化了艾薇 对吧\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Hold on a second. Enzo turns Ivy, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.57,0:15:41.60,中文,,0,0,0,,一个猎人杀了她 然后我倒成了坏人咯\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}A hunter kills her, and yet I'm the bad guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.61,0:15:43.11,中文,,0,0,0,,我不是那种 威胁要出卖别的吸血鬼\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I'm not the one threatening to turn in
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.11,0:15:45.03,中文,,0,0,0,,好来保住自己的人\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}other vampires to save his own skin.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.03,0:15:47.08,中文,,0,0,0,,唯一出卖吸血鬼给猎人的人\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}The only one who's turned in other vampires
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.08,0:15:49.11,中文,,0,0,0,,就是你 斯特凡\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}is you, Stephan.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.11,0:15:50.71,中文,,0,0,0,,所以你才过来帮忙\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}That's why you're helping...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.71,0:15:53.37,中文,,0,0,0,,你害达蒙的朋友被抓 你心虚了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Guilt for getting Damon's friend captured.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.37,0:15:56.35,中文,,0,0,0,,呵呵 达蒙是我哥 我第一个抛弃他\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Yeah. Damon is my brother, and I gave up on him first.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.35,0:15:57.49,中文,,0,0,0,,恩佐没有\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Enzo didn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.49,0:15:58.62,中文,,0,0,0,,所以如果救他的二货朋友\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}So if rescuing his idiot friend
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.62,0:15:59.96,中文,,0,0,0,,在某种程度上可以补偿他\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}is gonna somehow make it up to him,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.96,0:16:00.99,中文,,0,0,0,,那这件事就该由我来做\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}that's exactly what I'm gonna do.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.99,0:16:02.33,中文,,0,0,0,,很好 你觉悟了啊\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Great. Good for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.33,0:16:03.59,中文,,0,0,0,,你想好该怎么补偿我的时候\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Let me know when you figure out how you're
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.59,0:16:05.53,中文,,0,0,0,,跟我说一声啊\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}gonna make everything up to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.48,0:16:25.73,中文,,0,0,0,,我们进去看看\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Let's get in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.82,0:16:33.97,中文,,0,0,0,,他到底在哪儿\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Well, where the hell is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.76,0:16:42.57,中文,,0,0,0,,我喜欢你的手镯 什么材料做的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I like your bracelet. What is it made of?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.57,0:16:44.53,中文,,0,0,0,,不知道\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}No idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.53,0:16:46.74,中文,,0,0,0,,既然你在这儿 有些事情我能问问你的看法吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}While you're here, can I get your opinion on something?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.74,0:16:47.80,中文,,0,0,0,,当然 好啊\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Sure. Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.80,0:16:48.87,中文,,0,0,0,,一个女病人\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Female patient...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.87,0:16:51.44,中文,,0,0,0,,头部钝力创伤 大量内出血\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Blunt-force trauma to the head, massive internal hemorrhaging,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.44,0:16:53.81,中文,,0,0,0,,多处骨折\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}multiple bone fractures.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.81,0:16:56.00,中文,,0,0,0,,她是麦田迷宫的受害者\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}She was a victim at the corn maze.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.88,0:16:59.85,中文,,0,0,0,,可她在哪儿\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Where is she?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.85,0:17:02.48,中文,,0,0,0,,可能在上大一的文学课\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Probably freshman lit.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.49,0:17:04.39,中文,,0,0,0,,我不明白\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I don't get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.39,0:17:06.02,中文,,0,0,0,,我也不明白\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Neither do I.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.02,0:17:07.96,中文,,0,0,0,,瞧 这个病人其实一直没入院治疗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}See, the patient was never admitted,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.96,0:17:09.96,中文,,0,0,0,,即使受了这么严重的伤\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}even with such extensive injuries.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.96,0:17:11.99,中文,,0,0,0,,利亚姆说你当场给她紧急治疗了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Liam said you treated her at the scene.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.99,0:17:13.66,中文,,0,0,0,,对于一个只读了半学期医学预科的人来说\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}That's a pretty good save for someone
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.66,0:17:15.33,中文,,0,0,0,,真是了不起\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}with half a semester of pre-med.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.33,0:17:18.60,中文,,0,0,0,,好吧 我觉得他们\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Yeah. I think they were exaggerating
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.60,0:17:20.57,中文,,0,0,0,,夸大了她的伤情\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}how bad off she was.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.57,0:17:22.84,中文,,0,0,0,,当时天很暗 而且 到处是血\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}It was dark, and, yeah, there was a lot of blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.84,0:17:26.41,中文,,0,0,0,,别解释了 我知道阿拉里克的情况 我知道你的情况\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Don't. I know what Alaric is. I know what you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.41,0:17:28.48,中文,,0,0,0,,如果再有血袋消失\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}If any more blood bags go missing,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.48,0:17:31.55,中文,,0,0,0,,我知道要找谁\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I know who to come to.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.31,0:17:51.71,中文,,0,0,0,,某人做得真绝啊\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Well, somebody was thorough.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.99,0:18:03.45,中文,,0,0,0,,一张达蒙的照片都没有\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}No pictures of Damon anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.53,0:18:15.63,中文,,0,0,0,,噢\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Ohh...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.00,0:18:20.94,中文,,0,0,0,,你这样会吓死个人啊\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}It's kind of creepy, you just standing there
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.94,0:18:22.57,中文,,0,0,0,,站那儿一动不动 一声不吭\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}all hulky and brooding.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.57,0:18:26.41,中文,,0,0,0,,你倒先说起来了 跟踪我姐姐的怪蜀黍\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Says the freak who's stalking my sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.41,0:18:31.11,中文,,0,0,0,,严格来说 我是躺在这儿等\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Technically, I'm lying in wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.07,0:18:37.92,中文,,0,0,0,,邦妮为什么没回来\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Why didn't Bonnie come back?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.13,0:18:43.39,中文,,0,0,0,,她为什么没回来\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Why didn't she come back?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.30,0:18:47.97,中文,,0,0,0,,因为她不在那儿\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Because she wasn't there.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.97,0:18:50.00,中文,,0,0,0,,就我在那儿\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}It was just me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.04,0:19:00.08,中文,,0,0,0,,你知道我还在给她充话费\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}You know I paid her cell bill
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.08,0:19:01.88,中文,,0,0,0,,这样我就能每天打她电话\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}so I could call her phone and hear her say
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.88,0:19:04.28,中文,,0,0,0,,听她说同样的六个字吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}the same 6 words every day?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.42,0:19:09.35,中文,,0,0,0,,听起来不错 我也会打一个\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Sounds good. I'll give it a call.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.35,0:19:12.49,中文,,0,0,0,,为什么 她讨厌你\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Why? She hated you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.56,0:19:18.76,中文,,0,0,0,,邦妮没和我一起在那儿 杰里米\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Bonnie wasn't there with me, Jeremy,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.76,0:19:22.87,中文,,0,0,0,,因为她获得了安息\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}because she found peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.37,0:19:28.30,中文,,0,0,0,,她找到了更好的地方\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}She's in a better place.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.01,0:19:36.01,中文,,0,0,0,,你是怎么知道的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}How did you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.01,0:19:37.45,中文,,0,0,0,,一方面我不相信你\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Besides not believing that you closed
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.45,0:19:38.75,中文,,0,0,0,,能够在没有急救装备的情况下\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}a penetrating abdominal trauma
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.75,0:19:40.58,中文,,0,0,0,,缝合一个贯穿腹部的创伤\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}without so much as a first aid kit?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.59,0:19:43.65,中文,,0,0,0,,另外我非常确信你不是在我的咖啡里找甜叶菊\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Pretty sure you weren't looking for stevia in my coffee.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.66,0:19:45.29,中文,,0,0,0,,对于阿拉里克 我不是百分百的确定\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}With Alaric, I wasn't 100% certain
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.29,0:19:47.19,中文,,0,0,0,,他想要催眠我 但是接着我想起\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}he tried to compel me, but then I remembered
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.19,0:19:49.66,中文,,0,0,0,,我的爱情一直在走狗屎运\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I have really crappy luck in my love life.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.66,0:19:51.83,中文,,0,0,0,,所以必须的 我那火辣的恋人老师\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}So of course my hot, new teacher crush
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.83,0:19:53.36,中文,,0,0,0,,肯定是个吸血鬼\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}would be a vampire.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.36,0:19:55.80,中文,,0,0,0,,-那么你又是什么 -我很忙\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}- So then what are you? - Busy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.80,0:19:57.50,中文,,0,0,0,,如果你想要继续呆在这儿\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}If you want to stick around, there's food trays
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.50,0:19:59.34,中文,,0,0,0,,三楼有脏盘子 去刷干净\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}on the third floor that need clearing.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.34,0:20:02.14,中文,,0,0,0,,就这样么 你打算让我留在这儿\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}That's it? You're gonna let me stay?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.14,0:20:04.81,中文,,0,0,0,,你救了那个女孩 而不是吸她的血\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}You saved that girl instead of feeding on her.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.81,0:20:08.68,中文,,0,0,0,,-我看你还是挺好的 -对于这件事\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}- That's good enough for me. - You're not even afraid,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.68,0:20:11.35,中文,,0,0,0,,你甚至都不害怕 不担心\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}not ever fazed, for that matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.35,0:20:14.02,中文,,0,0,0,,只有一种人 能够在不需要马鞭草的情况下\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}There's only one thing that can resist compulsion
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.02,0:20:16.94,中文,,0,0,0,,抵抗吸血鬼的催眠 那就是女巫\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}without needing vervain, and that's a witch.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.09,0:20:22.19,中文,,0,0,0,,你是个女巫\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}You're a witch.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.19,0:20:24.66,中文,,0,0,0,,咱们做个交易怎么样\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}How about I make a deal with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.66,0:20:26.23,中文,,0,0,0,,你不要问关于我的问题\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}You don't ask questions about me,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.23,0:20:29.10,中文,,0,0,0,,我也不会问关于你的问题\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}and I won't ask questions about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.10,0:20:30.23,中文,,0,0,0,,成交\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.23,0:20:31.74,中文,,0,0,0,,噢 而且你可以告诉阿拉里克\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Oh, and you can tell Alaric,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.74,0:20:34.40,中文,,0,0,0,,如果他想避免一段凌乱的感情\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}if he wants to avoid a complicated relationship,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.41,0:20:38.96,中文,,0,0,0,,他不需要催眠任何人\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}he doesn't have to hide behind compulsion to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.99,0:20:50.22,中文,,0,0,0,,可能我没在这儿长大是件好事情\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Maybe it was a good thing I didn't grow up here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.22,0:20:51.99,中文,,0,0,0,,那么你从哪儿来呢\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}So where do you come from?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.99,0:20:53.26,中文,,0,0,0,,我每年都住在不同的地方\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Give me the year, and I'll give you
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.26,0:20:55.56,中文,,0,0,0,,寄养在不同的家庭\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}the town and foster home.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.56,0:20:58.90,中文,,0,0,0,,噢 真好\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Oh, good.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.90,0:21:00.63,中文,,0,0,0,,好像知道里面有什么\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Wonder what's in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.63,0:21:01.90,中文,,0,0,0,,锁住了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}It's locked.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.90,0:21:04.47,中文,,0,0,0,,锁住了意味着很重要\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Locked means important.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.11,0:21:12.39,中文,,0,0,0,,-嘿 卡罗 你找到他了吗 -没有 恩佐不在这儿\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}- Hey, Care, did you get him? - No. Enzo is not here.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.39,0:21:14.01,中文,,0,0,0,,除了这个明显的地点之外\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Any idea where Tripp might have taken him
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.01,0:21:16.71,中文,,0,0,0,,特里普还会把他带到哪去呢\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}besides the very obvious one?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.71,0:21:19.44,中文,,0,0,0,,等等 我看个东西\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Hang on. Let me see that.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.99,0:21:23.45,中文,,0,0,0,,卡罗琳 我们有新麻烦了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Caroline, we have another problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.45,0:21:26.46,中文,,0,0,0,,特里普收着艾薇的手机\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Tripp... Has Ivy's phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.46,0:21:28.39,中文,,0,0,0,,然后呢 我是说这家伙是个杀人狂\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}And? I mean, the guy is a murderer.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.39,0:21:30.39,中文,,0,0,0,,顺手牵羊对他来说小菜一碟\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Petty theft isn't much of a stretch.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.39,0:21:32.90,中文,,0,0,0,,但你的名字在\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Yeah, but your name is at the top
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.90,0:21:34.53,中文,,0,0,0,,最近通话记录的顶部\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}of the recent dialed list.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.90,0:21:37.43,中文,,0,0,0,,噢天哪 他知道我是什么了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Oh, my God, he knows what I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.43,0:21:41.40,中文,,0,0,0,,我猜他知道怎么找你了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I'm guessing he knows where to find you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.82,0:21:58.92,中文,,0,0,0,,是邦尼 请给我留言\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}It's Bonnie. Leave me a message.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.62,0:22:02.79,中文,,0,0,0,,就这样\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}That's it?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.79,0:22:05.63,中文,,0,0,0,,你的语音信息就这样吗 开什么玩笑\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}That's your outgoing message? Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.63,0:22:07.80,中文,,0,0,0,,我是说 我主动找寻你的声音的时候\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I mean, the one time I'm actively seeking
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.80,0:22:11.10,中文,,0,0,0,,我只找到了这个\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}the sound of your voice, that's all I get.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.10,0:22:14.60,中文,,0,0,0,,很好 嗯\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Perfect. Hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.60,0:22:18.27,中文,,0,0,0,,不管怎么样 我在你的屋子里\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Anyway, I'm in your room,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.27,0:22:21.71,中文,,0,0,0,,实际没听起来那么奇怪\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}which is a lot less weird than it sounds.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.71,0:22:24.28,中文,,0,0,0,,我只是想说\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I just wanted to say that
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.04,0:22:28.18,中文,,0,0,0,,因为你为我做了那么多\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}because of what you did for me,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.18,0:22:31.92,中文,,0,0,0,,今天我找到了埃琳娜\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}today is the day that I get to see Elena.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.99,0:22:34.49,中文,,0,0,0,,所以 谢谢\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}So thank you,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.56,0:22:39.63,中文,,0,0,0,,而且 我很抱歉\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}and I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.63,0:22:41.52,中文,,0,0,0,,除了这个我不知道要说什么了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Other than that, I don't know what to say
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.97,0:22:46.27,中文,,0,0,0,,或者说除了这个我应该说什么\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}or what I'm supposed to say except that,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.82,0:22:52.57,中文,,0,0,0,,听起来好像是绝不可能\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}defying all possible global scenarios,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.01,0:22:57.01,中文,,0,0,0,,但 我有一点想念你了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I might miss you a little bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.81,0:23:00.71,中文,,0,0,0,,噢 嘿 我得走了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Ooh, hey, I got to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.49,0:23:07.29,中文,,0,0,0,,所以你没有忘记我的电话号码么 这个开端不错\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}So you didn't forget my number. That's a good start.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.29,0:23:09.69,中文,,0,0,0,,是的 我猜我要按达蒙的按钮\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Yeah. I figured I'd press the Damon button
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.69,0:23:11.16,中文,,0,0,0,,看看会发生什么\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}and see what happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.16,0:23:15.68,中文,,0,0,0,,-现在怎么了 -我不知道\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}- And what is happening? - I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.68,0:23:17.57,中文,,0,0,0,,我都不知道我在做什么\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I don't even know what I'm doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.57,0:23:19.53,中文,,0,0,0,,我只是\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I just...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.54,0:23:23.37,中文,,0,0,0,,我觉得我们应该面对面地谈一次\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I'm thinking we should meet face to face.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.37,0:23:25.41,中文,,0,0,0,,我不能一直逃避你\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I can't run from you forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.41,0:23:28.21,中文,,0,0,0,,所以来我的宿舍吧\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}So come by my dorm?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.21,0:23:30.71,中文,,0,0,0,,好 好 我会到这儿的 那儿\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Yeah. Yeah. I'll be here. There.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.71,0:23:33.55,中文,,0,0,0,,我会去那儿的 一定 马上就去\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I'll be there, absolutely, in a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.55,0:23:37.02,中文,,0,0,0,,-马上见 -好的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}- See you in a little bit. - Ok.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.31,0:24:06.98,中文,,0,0,0,,你还挺快的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Well, that was fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.25,0:24:14.79,中文,,0,0,0,,啊\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Agh!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.16,0:24:20.46,中文,,0,0,0,,你是谁\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.90,0:24:25.23,中文,,0,0,0,,呃\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.23,0:24:27.23,中文,,0,0,0,,呃\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.87,0:24:51.11,中文,,0,0,0,,达蒙\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Damon?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.39,0:25:02.22,中文,,0,0,0,,埃琳娜 冷静\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Elena, calm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:02.22,0:25:04.12,中文,,0,0,0,,你只要去找卡罗琳 然后到达老米勒路\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Just find Caroline and get to old Miller road.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.12,0:25:05.72,中文,,0,0,0,,我们会把他带回来\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}We'll get him back.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.80,0:25:16.14,中文,,0,0,0,,我和埃琳娜进行了一段非常有趣的对话\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I had an interesting conversation with Elena.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.14,0:25:18.25,中文,,0,0,0,,是啊 我想听到全部内容 只是不是现在\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Yeah, and I want to hear all about it, just not right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.25,0:25:21.01,中文,,0,0,0,,急什么 紧急超自然课程么\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}What's the rush, occult studies emergency?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.01,0:25:22.17,中文,,0,0,0,,是的 我需要去某些地方\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Yeah. I have someplace I need to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:22.17,0:25:23.78,中文,,0,0,0,,所以如果你不介意\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}So if you don't mind...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.78,0:25:26.71,中文,,0,0,0,,你为什么不催眠我让路\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Why don't you just compel me out of the way?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.71,0:25:27.98,中文,,0,0,0,,你看 你不觉得已经到了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Look. Don't you think it's about time
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.98,0:25:29.65,中文,,0,0,0,,我们互相坦白的时候了吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}we level with each other?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:31.43,0:25:33.89,中文,,0,0,0,,好吧 这样怎么样\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Ok. How's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:33.89,0:25:36.62,中文,,0,0,0,,我最好的朋友 他刚刚复活\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}My best friend, he just came back from the dead,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:36.62,0:25:38.42,中文,,0,0,0,,但是我现在要赶在\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}but now I have to save him
Dialogue: 0,0:25:38.42,0:25:40.08,中文,,0,0,0,,他被一个吸血鬼猎手载着\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}from a vampire hunter before he's driven
Dialogue: 0,0:25:40.08,0:25:42.66,中文,,0,0,0,,越过反魔法界限 并再次被杀掉之前救他\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}across an antimagic border and killed again.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.66,0:25:45.06,中文,,0,0,0,,所以现在给你一点建议\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}So here's some friendly advice.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:45.06,0:25:47.13,中文,,0,0,0,,也许离我远点\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}It's probably a good idea to stay
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.13,0:25:49.83,中文,,0,0,0,,对你来说更好\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}as far away from me as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.61,0:26:04.48,中文,,0,0,0,,呃\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:04.48,0:26:08.49,中文,,0,0,0,,-早安啊 亲爱的 -恩佐\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}- Morning, sunshine. - Enzo?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:08.49,0:26:11.99,中文,,0,0,0,,嗯 这还真是怀念这个啊\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Well, this brings back memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:11.99,0:26:14.19,中文,,0,0,0,,我很高兴你想办法回来了 伙计\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I'm glad you found a way back, mate.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:14.19,0:26:16.13,中文,,0,0,0,,虽然恐怕这是一次短暂的相逢\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Afraid it's gonna be a short reunion, through.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:16.13,0:26:19.43,中文,,0,0,0,,我们要去神秘瀑布镇\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}We're headed to Mystic Falls, known for its bridges;
Dialogue: 0,0:26:19.43,0:26:21.20,中文,,0,0,0,,那个以桥和复古小镇魔法而出名的地方\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}quaint, small-town charm;
Dialogue: 0,0:26:21.20,0:26:24.64,中文,,0,0,0,,还有一个大大的吸血鬼控制问题\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}and a really big vampire bug zapper.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:24.64,0:26:27.47,中文,,0,0,0,,斯特凡本来可以告诉我镇子里有一个吸血鬼猎人的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Stefan could've told me there was a hunter in town.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:27.47,0:26:29.67,中文,,0,0,0,,也许他忘记了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}It probably slipped his mind because he's
Dialogue: 0,0:26:29.67,0:26:33.51,中文,,0,0,0,,因为我重新被关押是他的责任\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}responsible for my return to incarceration.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:33.51,0:26:35.28,中文,,0,0,0,,他为什么要这么做\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Why would he do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:35.28,0:26:37.48,中文,,0,0,0,,也许是嫉妒我的口音\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Probably jealous of my accent.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:37.48,0:26:38.88,中文,,0,0,0,,嗯 也许他这么做是因为\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Eh, maybe he did it because I killed
Dialogue: 0,0:26:38.88,0:26:40.48,中文,,0,0,0,,我杀了他的新女朋友\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}his new girlfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:40.49,0:26:42.99,中文,,0,0,0,,嗯 这就说得通了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Yeah. That'll do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:46.09,0:26:48.06,中文,,0,0,0,,抱歉 妈妈\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Sorry, mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:48.06,0:26:51.76,中文,,0,0,0,,伊莲娜在参加 疯狂汽车迷节目\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Elena is auditioning for "Top Gear."
Dialogue: 0,0:26:51.76,0:26:55.00,中文,,0,0,0,,嗯 没事\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Yeah. Ok.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:55.00,0:26:56.53,中文,,0,0,0,,拜\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:56.53,0:26:58.37,中文,,0,0,0,,所以 我妈妈正在关闭13号线路\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}So my mom is shutting down route 13.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:58.37,0:26:59.90,中文,,0,0,0,,军队还会再回来\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Tripp will have to double back,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:59.90,0:27:01.47,中文,,0,0,0,,然后只有两条穿过界线的路径\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}and there's only two other ways across the border.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:01.47,0:27:05.23,中文,,0,0,0,,你对轮胎有偏好吗 前面还是后面\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Do you have a tire preference... front, back?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:05.23,0:27:07.88,中文,,0,0,0,,没有 好的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}No? Ok.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:09.68,0:27:12.92,中文,,0,0,0,,这样做好像自然了点\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I think this sells a spinout.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:12.92,0:27:16.09,中文,,0,0,0,,你觉得呢 埃琳娜\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}What do you think? Elena?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:18.25,0:27:20.50,中文,,0,0,0,,我想要回我的记忆\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I want my memories back.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:20.86,0:27:23.93,中文,,0,0,0,,等等 什么\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Wait. What?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:23.93,0:27:26.36,中文,,0,0,0,,我决定了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I made up my mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:26.36,0:27:28.50,中文,,0,0,0,,如果这次达蒙没死\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}If Damon survives this,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:28.50,0:27:32.60,中文,,0,0,0,,我就要阿拉里克解除掉催眠\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}then I want Alaric to uncompel me.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:32.60,0:27:36.11,中文,,0,0,0,,我是说 我不能想象爱过他\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I mean, I can't imagine ever loving him.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:36.11,0:27:40.44,中文,,0,0,0,,我也不能为了回避事实\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I also can't ignore
Dialogue: 0,0:27:40.44,0:27:44.15,中文,,0,0,0,,而只忽略掉我不喜欢的部分\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}the parts I don't like just to avoid the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:44.15,0:27:46.92,中文,,0,0,0,,我的意思是 如果我只知道一半的故事\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I mean, how would I make any decisions
Dialogue: 0,0:27:46.92,0:27:50.62,中文,,0,0,0,,我怎么能做出任何决定\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}if I only know half the story?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:12.24,0:28:14.94,中文,,0,0,0,,你不需要拆掉引擎\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}You don't have to take apart the whole engine.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:14.95,0:28:18.08,中文,,0,0,0,,我们只需要引诱特里普进来 这样就能救他们\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}We just need to lure Tripp in so we can grab them.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:20.98,0:28:23.50,中文,,0,0,0,,你知道的 这不是你的错\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}You know, it's not your fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:23.99,0:28:26.39,中文,,0,0,0,,这就是\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Pretty much is.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:26.95,0:28:29.12,中文,,0,0,0,,听着 你不是唯一一个放弃了的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Look. You're not the only one who gave up.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:31.93,0:28:33.92,中文,,0,0,0,,过去四个月的每一秒\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Every second for the last 4 months,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:33.92,0:28:36.00,中文,,0,0,0,,我想到的只有\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}all I could think about was when I'm gonna get
Dialogue: 0,0:28:36.00,0:28:38.17,中文,,0,0,0,,我什么时候能再喝到血\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}my next sip of blood, when am I gonna
Dialogue: 0,0:28:38.17,0:28:40.94,中文,,0,0,0,,我什么时候能弄糟一切 伤害到某些人\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}screw up and hurt somebody,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:40.94,0:28:42.27,中文,,0,0,0,,我复活过来\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}why did I come back to life
Dialogue: 0,0:28:42.27,0:28:45.17,中文,,0,0,0,,就是要做这样的事\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}just to be this thing,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:45.18,0:28:48.18,中文,,0,0,0,,我一度猎杀吸血鬼\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}that I used to hunt vampires
Dialogue: 0,0:28:48.18,0:28:50.07,中文,,0,0,0,,突然 我成了吸血鬼的一员\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}and suddenly, I was one.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:52.16,0:28:54.48,中文,,0,0,0,,寻找达蒙是唯一\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Searching for Damon was the only thing
Dialogue: 0,0:28:54.48,0:28:57.19,中文,,0,0,0,,能让我不再想这些的事\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}that could take my mind off of it,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:57.19,0:29:01.66,中文,,0,0,0,,但是我基本上要把任务当做让我分心的东西\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}but I was basically going through the motions
Dialogue: 0,0:29:01.66,0:29:07.03,中文,,0,0,0,,因为 说实话 斯特凡\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}as a distraction because, honestly, Stefan,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:07.03,0:29:09.90,中文,,0,0,0,,我也会放弃的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I'd given up, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:15.00,0:29:17.84,中文,,0,0,0,,来了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}There.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:17.84,0:29:19.94,中文,,0,0,0,,那就是他  你要待在车里\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}That's him. You should stay in the car.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:19.94,0:29:22.34,中文,,0,0,0,,-他知道你长得什么样子 -他认为我是他那边的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}- He knows what you look like. - He thinks I'm on his side.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:22.35,0:29:24.01,中文,,0,0,0,,是啊 但是恩佐可能出卖了你\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Yeah, unless Enzo told him different.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:24.01,0:29:26.25,中文,,0,0,0,,去告诉埃琳娜他在这里\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Go tell Elena he's here.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:35.32,0:29:37.46,中文,,0,0,0,,晚上好\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Evening.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:37.46,0:29:39.49,中文,,0,0,0,,要带我的朋友去单身聚会\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Tried to get my buddy to a bachelor party,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:39.50,0:29:41.03,中文,,0,0,0,,我们的车不走了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}and our car just stopped.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:41.03,0:29:42.63,中文,,0,0,0,,你能帮帮我们么\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}You think you can help us out?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:42.63,0:29:44.57,中文,,0,0,0,,嗯 我对车一窍不通\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Uh, don't know anything about cars.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:44.57,0:29:45.87,中文,,0,0,0,,是的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:45.87,0:29:48.90,中文,,0,0,0,,嗯 也许你能载我一段\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Well, maybe you could give us a ride, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:48.91,0:29:50.24,中文,,0,0,0,,那是谁\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Who's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:50.24,0:29:54.04,中文,,0,0,0,,里克 他肯定是有计划\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Ric. He's up to something.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:54.04,0:29:56.91,中文,,0,0,0,,肯定是好事 他还欠我一个人情\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Better be good. Bastard owes me.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:56.91,0:29:59.61,中文,,0,0,0,,抱歉 有点赶时间\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Sorry. In a bit of a hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:59.62,0:30:02.43,中文,,0,0,0,,是啊 我们也是\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Yeah. So are we.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:04.55,0:30:06.29,中文,,0,0,0,,啊\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Uh!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:06.29,0:30:09.42,中文,,0,0,0,,啊 噢\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Uh! Ooh!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:22.40,0:30:24.87,中文,,0,0,0,,噢\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:32.23,0:30:37.89,中文,,0,0,0,,啊 啊 啊 啊\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Uh! Uh! Ugh! Agh!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:39.97,0:30:41.81,中文,,0,0,0,,斯特凡\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Stefan.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:44.51,0:30:46.18,中文,,0,0,0,,斯特凡 怎么了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Stefan, what's happening?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:46.18,0:30:49.48,中文,,0,0,0,,达蒙和阿拉里克越过了边境\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Damon and Alaric are across the border.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:49.49,0:30:52.12,中文,,0,0,0,,我得挂了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I got to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:52.12,0:30:54.52,中文,,0,0,0,,哦 天哪\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Oh, my God.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:02.40,0:31:08.14,中文,,0,0,0,,啊 啊啊\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Agh! Ugh! Aagh!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:08.14,0:31:10.74,中文,,0,0,0,,啊\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:15.88,0:31:18.78,中文,,0,0,0,,我回来可不是为了这样子\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I came back for this?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:18.78,0:31:20.72,中文,,0,0,0,,看着自己慢慢死去\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Consumption wasn't much fun
Dialogue: 0,0:31:20.72,0:31:23.48,中文,,0,0,0,,并不是很有趣\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}the first time around, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:30.36,0:31:32.23,中文,,0,0,0,,没事了 我在这儿\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}It's ok. I'm here.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:32.23,0:31:33.39,中文,,0,0,0,,怎么\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}How?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:33.40,0:31:36.03,中文,,0,0,0,,像个疯狂的跟踪者一样跟踪你\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Followed you like a crazy stalker,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:36.03,0:31:37.83,中文,,0,0,0,,可不是什么好差事\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}not one of my finer moments.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:37.83,0:31:41.35,中文,,0,0,0,,不不 抓住他\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}No, no. Get him.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:53.58,0:31:56.85,中文,,0,0,0,,你一定要让我回到边境那边去\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}You have to get me across the border.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:56.85,0:31:59.75,中文,,0,0,0,,它在消除魔力 我会死掉的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}It's stripping away the magic. I'll die.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:59.75,0:32:01.59,中文,,0,0,0,,如果我动了你 你会死的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}You'll die if I move you.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:01.59,0:32:03.36,中文,,0,0,0,,我需要止血\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I have to stop the bleeding.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:03.36,0:32:04.99,中文,,0,0,0,,划破了你下面的主动脉\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Nicked your descending aorta.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:04.99,0:32:06.76,中文,,0,0,0,,我知道 这就是会弄死我的东西\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I know. That's what killed me.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:06.76,0:32:08.93,中文,,0,0,0,,你没有让我回来 是吧\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}You didn't have me back then, did you,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:08.93,0:32:11.16,中文,,0,0,0,,并且你也没有止血纱布\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}and you didn't have hemostatic gauze.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:11.17,0:32:15.07,中文,,0,0,0,,起来 快点 起来\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Get up. Come on. Get up.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:23.31,0:32:24.91,中文,,0,0,0,,啊\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Ugh!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:30.32,0:32:32.89,中文,,0,0,0,,怎么了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}What's happening?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:32.89,0:32:35.36,中文,,0,0,0,,你还清醒着吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}You still with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:35.36,0:32:37.09,中文,,0,0,0,,我在处理这个伤口的时候\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}While I'm sealing this wound,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:37.09,0:32:38.59,中文,,0,0,0,,我想要你想一想\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I want you to think about how you tried
Dialogue: 0,0:32:38.59,0:32:40.26,中文,,0,0,0,,你当时多么努力的迷惑学校里最聪明的女生\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}to compel one of the smartest women on campus
Dialogue: 0,0:32:40.26,0:32:42.39,中文,,0,0,0,,让她忘记她和你的约会\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}to forget about her date with you,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:42.40,0:32:44.76,中文,,0,0,0,,那次我单打独斗救了几十个生命的约会\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}the date where I single-handedly saved
Dialogue: 0,0:32:44.77,0:32:49.60,中文,,0,0,0,,而我甚至连妆都没花\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}dozens of lives without smearing my makeup.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:49.60,0:32:53.31,中文,,0,0,0,,阿拉里克 坚持住\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Alaric? Hang on.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:53.31,0:32:55.61,中文,,0,0,0,,别走\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Stay with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:55.61,0:32:58.98,中文,,0,0,0,,拜托 心快跳起来啊\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Come on. Gonna get that heart pumping.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:58.98,0:33:03.25,中文,,0,0,0,,你还没对我说你想说的话呢\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}You don't get to have the last word with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:03.25,0:33:05.15,中文,,0,0,0,,阿拉里克\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Alaric!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:07.15,0:33:09.76,中文,,0,0,0,,阿拉里克\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Alaric!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:16.53,0:33:19.30,中文,,0,0,0,,别走\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Stay with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:19.30,0:33:22.17,中文,,0,0,0,,拜托\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:25.77,0:33:28.34,中文,,0,0,0,,啊\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Ah...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:28.34,0:33:31.01,中文,,0,0,0,,啊\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Ah...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:31.01,0:33:34.91,中文,,0,0,0,,有  有 有点不对劲\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}So... so... Something is wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:34.92,0:33:36.45,中文,,0,0,0,,-别动 -不\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}- Don't move. - No.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:36.45,0:33:38.82,中文,,0,0,0,,有点不对劲\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Something is wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:38.82,0:33:40.99,中文,,0,0,0,,我不应该活下来\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I'm not supposed to be alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:40.99,0:33:43.06,中文,,0,0,0,,你也没有理由死掉\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}There's no reason you shouldn't be.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:43.06,0:33:44.92,中文,,0,0,0,,我封住了伤口\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I sealed the wound.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:44.93,0:33:48.39,中文,,0,0,0,,我们现在得送你去医院\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}We just have to get you to the hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:57.74,0:33:58.84,中文,,0,0,0,,嗯 我会告诉他\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Yeah. I'll tell her.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:58.84,0:34:00.54,中文,,0,0,0,,字幕\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:02.71,0:34:05.35,中文,,0,0,0,,我刚刚在9号路线\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I was just at route 9,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:05.35,0:34:07.08,中文,,0,0,0,,出现了一次撞击 但是他们不在那儿\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}and there was a crash, but they weren't there.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:07.08,0:34:08.18,中文,,0,0,0,,是的 我知道\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Yeah. I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:08.18,0:34:09.75,中文,,0,0,0,,他们离开那儿了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}They had to get out of there.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:09.75,0:34:12.15,中文,,0,0,0,,发生什么了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:12.16,0:34:15.29,中文,,0,0,0,,斯特凡说\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Stefan said that...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:15.29,0:34:17.76,中文,,0,0,0,,什么 卡罗琳 什么\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}What, Caroline? What?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:20.00,0:34:24.13,中文,,0,0,0,,阿拉里克跨过了边境\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Alaric crossed the border,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:24.13,0:34:27.40,中文,,0,0,0,,但是乔在那边 她救了他\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}but Jo was there, and she saved him.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:28.74,0:34:31.74,中文,,0,0,0,,所以他没事\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}So he's ok.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:31.74,0:34:33.71,中文,,0,0,0,,这说明他还好 是吧\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}That means he's ok, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:33.71,0:34:36.04,中文,,0,0,0,,是的 伊莲娜 他没事\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Yeah, Elena. He's ok.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:36.05,0:34:40.32,中文,,0,0,0,,那你为什么是那种表情的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Then why do you have that look on your face?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:40.32,0:34:42.75,中文,,0,0,0,,发生什么了 卡罗琳\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}What happened, Caroline?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:42.75,0:34:44.69,中文,,0,0,0,,所有魔法都消失了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}All the magic stripped away,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:44.69,0:34:48.42,中文,,0,0,0,,但是乔在他死之前救了他\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}but Jo saved him just before he died.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:48.42,0:34:50.19,中文,,0,0,0,,什么\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:50.19,0:34:53.43,中文,,0,0,0,,我听不懂你在说什么 卡罗琳\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I don't know what that means, Caroline.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:53.43,0:34:57.23,中文,,0,0,0,,阿拉里克不再是吸血鬼了 埃琳娜\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Alaric is not a vampire anymore, Elena.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:57.23,0:34:59.30,中文,,0,0,0,,他已经是个普通人了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}He's human.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:04.44,0:35:06.61,中文,,0,0,0,,谢谢你载我一程\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Thanks for the ride. Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:06.61,0:35:08.11,中文,,0,0,0,,我觉得我只是省去了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I thought I'd save you the trouble
Dialogue: 0,0:35:08.11,0:35:10.28,中文,,0,0,0,,你再偷一辆车的麻烦\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}of having to boost another car.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:10.28,0:35:12.05,中文,,0,0,0,,真好笑\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}That was almost funny.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:12.05,0:35:14.75,中文,,0,0,0,,不过你还可以在搞笑些的 多诺万\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Hope for you yet, Donovan.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:14.75,0:35:17.75,中文,,0,0,0,,如果我告诉你我了解你的家族\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}If I told you I knew about your family,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:17.75,0:35:19.75,中文,,0,0,0,,你能接受一个小小的友好的建议吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}promise to take a little friendly advice?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:19.76,0:35:21.26,中文,,0,0,0,,等等\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Hang on.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:21.26,0:35:22.69,中文,,0,0,0,,你了解我的家族\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}You know who my family is?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:22.69,0:35:23.93,中文,,0,0,0,,我翻阅了关于这个镇上\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Read any history book
Dialogue: 0,0:35:23.93,0:35:25.56,中文,,0,0,0,,创始成员的所有历史书\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}about the town's founding members.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:25.56,0:35:27.36,中文,,0,0,0,,住在这间屋里的人\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}The guys that live in this house
Dialogue: 0,0:35:27.36,0:35:30.20,中文,,0,0,0,,是塞尔瓦托兄弟 达蒙和斯特凡\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}are Damon and Stefan Salvatore.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:30.20,0:35:32.47,中文,,0,0,0,,为什么你要现在告诉我这些\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Why are you just telling me this now?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:32.47,0:35:35.37,中文,,0,0,0,,因为\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Because...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:35.37,0:35:37.81,中文,,0,0,0,,他们是吸血鬼 不论他们去哪\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}They're vampires, and wherever they go,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:37.81,0:35:39.64,中文,,0,0,0,,总会带来死亡和痛苦\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}death and pain always follow.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:39.64,0:35:41.74,中文,,0,0,0,,所以如果你要找关于家族的事情\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}So if you're looking for family,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:41.74,0:35:43.78,中文,,0,0,0,,在这你是不会有发现的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}you're not gonna find it here.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:43.78,0:35:45.25,中文,,0,0,0,,就当帮你自己个忙\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Do yourself a favor and get
Dialogue: 0,0:35:45.25,0:35:47.25,中文,,0,0,0,,离这越远越好吧\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}as far away from this place as you can.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:47.25,0:35:48.98,中文,,0,0,0,,给点力啊\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:51.02,0:35:54.52,中文,,0,0,0,,不 真该死\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}No. Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:54.52,0:35:56.29,中文,,0,0,0,,杰\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Jer...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:56.29,0:35:58.73,中文,,0,0,0,,我一直尝试着注销掉邦妮的电话\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I keep trying to cancel Bonnie's phone,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:58.73,0:36:02.13,中文,,0,0,0,,但是没有她的pin码 我办不到\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}but I can't without her pin.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:02.13,0:36:04.17,中文,,0,0,0,,为什么我记不起她的pin码\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Why can't I remember her pin?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:04.17,0:36:06.67,中文,,0,0,0,,啊\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Uh!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:12.47,0:36:14.18,中文,,0,0,0,,啊 啊\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Uh! Uh!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:14.18,0:36:15.84,中文,,0,0,0,,放开我 放开我\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Get off! Get off!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:15.84,0:36:18.61,中文,,0,0,0,,嘿 没事了 不 不是的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Hey, it's ok. No, it's not!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:22.18,0:36:24.45,中文,,0,0,0,,她不在了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}She's gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:25.52,0:36:27.85,中文,,0,0,0,,邦妮不在了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Bonnie is gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:30.62,0:36:34.83,中文,,0,0,0,,乔是个好保姆 感觉怎么样\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Jo is a keeper. How does it feel?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:34.83,0:36:37.03,中文,,0,0,0,,噢 真疼啊\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Oh, it hurts a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:37.03,0:36:39.57,中文,,0,0,0,,在神秘瀑布没有一个吸血鬼可以帮着去治疗你\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Well, it's too bad there aren't any vampires in Mystic Falls
Dialogue: 0,0:36:39.57,0:36:41.34,中文,,0,0,0,,真是太糟糕了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}to help heal you.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:41.34,0:36:44.71,中文,,0,0,0,,好吧 我觉得他们给我滴注了吗啡\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Well, I think they got me on a morphine drip.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:44.71,0:36:47.52,中文,,0,0,0,,这是接来下最好的事了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}It's the next best thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:48.86,0:36:52.68,中文,,0,0,0,,埃琳娜 我很抱歉\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Elena, I'm so sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:52.68,0:36:54.55,中文,,0,0,0,,不 阿拉里克\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}No. No, Alaric.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:54.55,0:36:57.62,中文,,0,0,0,,看到你没事我很开心\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I'm just glad that you're ok.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:57.62,0:36:59.89,中文,,0,0,0,,我是说 直到一个小时前\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I mean, up until an hour ago,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:59.89,0:37:02.72,中文,,0,0,0,,我都不想恢复我的记忆\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I didn't even want my memories to return.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:02.72,0:37:04.96,中文,,0,0,0,,是我做了那个失去他们的决定\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I was the one who made the choice to lose them.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:04.96,0:37:08.03,中文,,0,0,0,,现在我必须面对\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Now I have to live with the fact
Dialogue: 0,0:37:08.03,0:37:11.73,中文,,0,0,0,,无法把他们再还给我的现实\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}that you can't give them back to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:11.73,0:37:13.70,中文,,0,0,0,,我知道你有多讨厌成为一个吸血鬼\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I know how much you hated being a vampire.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:13.70,0:37:17.20,中文,,0,0,0,,所以我很开心我们中的一个人达成了我们大家的心愿\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}So I'm just glad one of us got what we wanted.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:17.21,0:37:19.10,中文,,0,0,0,,那你想要的到底是什么呢\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}And what is it that you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:21.75,0:37:25.41,中文,,0,0,0,,能够看着达蒙的眼睛\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}To be able to look Damon in the eye,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:25.41,0:37:27.35,中文,,0,0,0,,知道所有我想知道\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}knowing all that I know
Dialogue: 0,0:37:27.35,0:37:30.53,中文,,0,0,0,,和我不想知道的一切\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}and all that I don't, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:33.38,0:37:36.16,中文,,0,0,0,,还有看看我对他有什么感觉\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}See how I feel about him.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:36.16,0:37:40.23,中文,,0,0,0,,我想相信我的感觉\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I want to trust how I feel.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:40.23,0:37:44.30,中文,,0,0,0,,我希望你能行 祝你好运 好吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I hope that you can. Good luck, ok?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:49.54,0:37:51.14,中文,,0,0,0,,这家医院烂透了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}This hospital sucks.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:51.15,0:37:53.31,中文,,0,0,0,,我不敢相信有人能活着出院\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I can't believe anyone actually makes it out alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:53.32,0:37:54.57,中文,,0,0,0,,一般没人活着出去\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}They usually don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:54.57,0:37:56.74,中文,,0,0,0,,我尽快把你转移到惠特默尔去\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I'm having you transferred to Whitmore ASAP.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:56.74,0:37:58.95,中文,,0,0,0,,谢谢你\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:58.95,0:38:01.29,中文,,0,0,0,,我只是做我该做的事\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Just doing my job.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:01.29,0:38:03.76,中文,,0,0,0,,嘿\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:04.58,0:38:07.40,中文,,0,0,0,,你做的可不止这些\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}You did more than that.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:07.40,0:38:08.93,中文,,0,0,0,,你让我重获新生\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}You gave me back my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:10.32,0:38:13.20,中文,,0,0,0,,多谢\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:18.28,0:38:22.54,中文,,0,0,0,,我当时只有一步之遥 一步之遥啊\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I was this close, this close.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:22.55,0:38:25.41,中文,,0,0,0,,我知道 我很抱歉\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I know. I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:25.42,0:38:27.75,中文,,0,0,0,,哦 我懂了 每个人都感到抱歉\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Oh, I got it. Everybody is sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:27.75,0:38:29.45,中文,,0,0,0,,你很抱歉你对我绝望\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}You're sorry you gave up on me,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:29.45,0:38:31.69,中文,,0,0,0,,你很抱歉把恩佐出卖给了猎人\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}sorry you turned Enzo in to that hunter guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:31.69,0:38:33.06,中文,,0,0,0,,里克对那次催眠感到抱歉\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Ric is sorry for the compulsion.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:33.06,0:38:34.46,中文,,0,0,0,,我相信如果埃琳娜能记起所有\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I'm sure if Elena could remember anything,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:34.46,0:38:35.79,中文,,0,0,0,,她也会感到抱歉的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}she'd be sorry, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:35.79,0:38:37.93,中文,,0,0,0,,你要理解这对她来说有多艰难\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}You got to understand how hard it was for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:37.93,0:38:40.80,中文,,0,0,0,,听到这些我都不耐烦了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I am so tired of hearing about how hard it was for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:40.80,0:38:43.12,中文,,0,0,0,,我也很艰难啊\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}It was hard for me, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:43.12,0:38:45.30,中文,,0,0,0,,至少你知道你有家可回\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}At least you knew you had a home to come back to.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:45.30,0:38:47.98,中文,,0,0,0,,她一无所有了 对她来说 你已经消失了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}She didn't have anything. To her, you were just gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:48.84,0:38:50.57,中文,,0,0,0,,那就假设我消失了吧\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Guess I still am.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:53.08,0:38:55.92,中文,,0,0,0,,里克说自从她忘记我之后过的很快乐\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Ric said she's happy without me since she's erased me.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:55.92,0:38:59.25,中文,,0,0,0,,你知道吗 我不想她快乐\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}You know what? I don't want her to be happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:59.25,0:39:03.12,中文,,0,0,0,,我想让她变得和我一样悲惨\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I want her to be miserable just like I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:03.12,0:39:05.29,中文,,0,0,0,,说完了吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}You done?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:05.29,0:39:07.12,中文,,0,0,0,,完了 不错\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}- Yeah. I'm done. - Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:07.12,0:39:09.26,中文,,0,0,0,,不要再拖时间了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Now quit stalling.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:09.26,0:39:11.66,中文,,0,0,0,,有个女孩你要去见见\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}There's a girl you need to go see.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:11.66,0:39:14.30,中文,,0,0,0,,如果它没效果怎么办\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}What if it doesn't work?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:14.30,0:39:15.80,中文,,0,0,0,,如果我们所拥有的不够强大\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}What if what we had isn't strong enough
Dialogue: 0,0:39:15.80,0:39:17.60,中文,,0,0,0,,去打破催眠怎么办\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}to break the compulsion?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:17.60,0:39:21.84,中文,,0,0,0,,那你是只想坐在这而不去解决事情吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}You're not gonna find out just sitting there, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:23.52,0:39:26.71,中文,,0,0,0,,我还是呆在这里吧\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Here goes everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:36.41,0:39:38.82,中文,,0,0,0,,嗨\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:40.12,0:39:42.79,中文,,0,0,0,,嗨\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:42.79,0:39:45.39,中文,,0,0,0,,那么\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}So...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:45.40,0:39:47.46,中文,,0,0,0,,我是斯特凡道歉之旅上\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Am I your last stop
Dialogue: 0,0:39:47.46,0:39:50.27,中文,,0,0,0,,的最后一站吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}on the Stefan Salvatore apology tour?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:50.27,0:39:55.44,中文,,0,0,0,,我们能不能把这事忘记\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Could we just get past this, please?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:55.85,0:39:59.94,中文,,0,0,0,,-我一直在尝试 -听着 卡罗琳\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}- I'm trying to. - Look, Caroline.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:59.94,0:40:02.21,中文,,0,0,0,,你想让我做什么 嗯\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}What do you want me to do, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:02.21,0:40:03.68,中文,,0,0,0,,不要再让我瞎想了 告诉我我该做什么\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Stop making me guess and tell me
Dialogue: 0,0:40:03.68,0:40:06.35,中文,,0,0,0,,能让我们做回朋友\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}so we can go back to being friends again.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:07.45,0:40:10.25,中文,,0,0,0,,好吧 现在是这样的 斯特凡\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Yeah. Well, that's the thing, Stefan.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:10.25,0:40:13.45,中文,,0,0,0,,经历过这些之后\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}After all of this, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:15.46,0:40:18.15,中文,,0,0,0,,我不想再和你做朋友了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I don't want to be friends anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:59.55,0:42:04.46,中文,,0,0,0,,
